	                                <p>Hey there!</p><p>Sorry for the late reply! You're right that buildForm returns nothing :). But that's ok! It's purpose is to modify the `$builder` variable that is passed in. So basically:</p><p>1) Symfony creates this `$builder` variable<br>2) Symfony calls buildForm() and passes you this variable<br>3) You modify this by adding fields with add()<br>4) Symfony uses the modified `$builder` to build your form</p><p>Does that make sense?</p><p>Cheers!</p>
